email_chain.body:
Dear Mr. Belanova,
Following your email from 27 August regarding the diesel delivery, I would need some additional details:
1. A different carrier name than Valeriano, along with its sailing schedule to Santos;
2. An estimate for the next delivery, with confirmation required next week;
3. Cargo delivery specifications such as max. speed, load line draft;
4. Confirmation of readiness for next delivery;
5. Details on any bunker surcharges;
6. Expected ETA in Santos and the date of payment;
7. Please email me the requested information at your earliest convenience.
Thank you in advance.
Best regards,
Florent
